OL,3,CBritish woman detained in Iran resumes
OL,4,Chunger strike
OL,6,FA British woman detained in an Iranian
OL,7,Fprison has resumed a hunger strike
OL,8,Fafter more than sixteen months in
OL,9,Fcustody, as her partner enters his
OL,10,Ftwelfth day without food in an
OL,11,Fescalating protest against their
OL,12,Fimprisonment.
OL,14,FCraig Foreman, a carpenter, and
OL,15,FLindsay Foreman, a life coach from
OL,16,FEast Sussex, were arrested in January
OL,17,F2025 while travelling through Iran on
OL,18,Fa round-the-world motorcycle journey.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
