PN,31802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779307554
OL,3,CBritish woman detained in Iran resumes
OL,4,Chunger strike
OL,6,FThe couple were later sentenced to ten
OL,7,Fyears in prison on espionage charges
OL,8,Fthey vehemently deny.
OL,10,FITV News has established that Mr
OL,11,FForeman has refused food since May 9,
OL,12,Fdespite receiving warnings from jail
OL,13,Fofficials that the protest breached
OL,14,Fthe terms of his imprisonment. Mrs
OL,15,FForeman is believed to have joined the
OL,16,Fhunger strike on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
