PN,31803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779307554
OL,3,CBritish woman detained in Iran resumes
OL,4,Chunger strike
OL,6,FThe couple's access to prison phones
OL,7,Fin Tehran's Evin prison was cut off
OL,8,Fearlier this month following a media
OL,9,Finterview they gave from custody,
OL,10,Fmeaning they are no longer allowed to
OL,11,Fupdate family members about their
OL,12,Fconditions.
OL,14,FMr Foreman is thought to have begun
OL,15,Fhis protest shortly after calls with
OL,16,Floved ones were withdrawn.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
