OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779307554
OL,3,CBritish woman detained in Iran resumes
OL,4,Chunger strike
OL,6,FTightly controlled phone access
OL,7,Fbetween the couple and the outside
OL,8,Fworld had been used to intensify
OL,9,Fpsychological pressure during their
OL,10,Fdetention, family members have said.
OL,12,FIn February, the Foreign Office
OL,13,Ftemporarily withdrew British staff
OL,14,Ffrom Iran due to fears of US and
OL,15,FIsraeli strikes against the country.
OL,16,FThe UK government continues to advise
OL,17,Fagainst all travel to Iran, warning of
OL,18,Fa "significant risk of arrest,
OL,19,Fquestioning or detention".
