OL,3,CBritish woman detained in Iran resumes
OL,4,Chunger strike
OL,6,FThe Foremans granted a series of
OL,7,Finterviews to ITV News from prison,
OL,8,Fbefore their phone access was cut.
OL,9,FLindsay Foreman said she had come to
OL,10,Fterms with the possibility she might
OL,11,Fdie in prison, fearing conflict in the
OL,12,Fregion could leave nobody inside the
OL,13,FIranian system willing or able to
OL,14,Fsecure their release.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
