OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1779307554
OL,3,CBritish woman detained in Iran resumes
OL,4,Chunger strike
OL,6,F"The first day you could feel it ` the
OL,7,Fimpact of the bombs, the rockets, the
OL,8,Fmissiles. The building shook. I was
OL,9,Factually on the phone to Joe when one
OL,10,Fof the bombs struck quite close by."
OL,12,FIn a separate interview, Craig Foreman
OL,13,Fsaid his message to the British
OL,14,Fgovernment was a simple one: "Help.
OL,15,FFull stop.
OL,17,F"I don't understand why we have been
OL,18,Fhere for 13 months, being held hostage
OL,19,Fin 2026. In what day and age does this
OL,20,Fhappen? When does this end?"
